data.description: 3 Bedrooms, 1 and 1 1/2 baths, Extra large living rm w/fireplace and open to an L shaped dining room, the openness makes the casualness very livable. Kitchen has lots of cabinet storage and a small eating area. Hardwood floors in all bedrooms.  Lower level Family room is wonderfully tucked behind a door to keep main level nice and quiet. Huge 2 1/2 car garage, Roof is 9 years old, CAC/Furnace replaced in 2018, New Electrical Box with 200 amp service is 5 yrs old, tankless Hot Water Heater is 3 years old, Dishwasher 1 year old, Washer 4 yrs, Dryer 7 years old.  Only 5 minutes to I-88 and minutes to train and so convenient for shopping, and schools.  You will love this location, Home "As is" but everything is in working condition and lots of news.  Owners out of state.  See All mechanical updates in remarks. FHA NOT ACCEPTED because 2.5  Garage siding is in old and has peeling paint.
